{"type": "article", "id": 58096, "title": "一款应急移动电源，也可以当置物架用｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-07T22:51:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48132, "name": "Momocca"}, {"id": 54041, "name": "Sugita Ace"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 54042, "name": "Pushkin Sonkusare"}, {"id": 54043, "name": "Sangwook Lee"}, {"id": 54044, "name": "Josh Owen"}, {"id": 54045, "name": "Wendell Castle"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181107215716Yi3D1LogwTfIzScW.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>denqul by Nendo for Sugita Ace</h3><p>日本设计工作室 Nendo 最近为多次合作过的日本品牌 Sugita Ace 设计了一款应急移动电源 denqul 。</p><p>在遇到灾害的时候，有电的智能手机能够保证基本的通信和照明，而移动电源能够为手机提供持续的电能。这款移动电源可事先在家中充好电，在遇到紧急情况时可以立刻取用，而非一直携带在身上。充电底座同时还可以作为放置眼镜和文具的置物架使用。</p><p>针对停电情况，设计原本打算使用太阳能板和手摇装置的方案，但最终采用了一种新的方法：仅用单手操作就可以有效进行发电。电源的杆身可抽拉至双倍长度并弯折为 L 型，使用者可借助离心力的作用，通过单手摇动来制造电能。电源顶端还装置了锂电池，能够使离心力最大化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=m07879r48yz\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215854iv8gHymENlhGckJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072158546c9sqbfAiDOYk03S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215855r0MPy3iYTWOm28pu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215855CDEz6bK0gAnhWxB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215855fvZAQDzWM4Eh0JoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072158550L64hJAiFk9sCl7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215856yD864EvJTa5uUkx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107215854X6jvdf5tasy7uiZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Sugita Ace</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Julia by Momocca</h3><p>购买家具的一个疑问是，你买一件家具不可能是一劳永逸的解决方案，要搬家怎么办？需求发生变化怎么办？</p><p>在最近的瓦伦西亚家具展览会 FeriaHábitatValenia 上，本土家具品牌 Momocca 推出了一种名为 Julia 的新型模块化家具系统，意在使用优质材料和精致的设计美学，提供模块化的、可自由组合、无限延展的家具解决方案。</p><p>Julia 系列使用金色和铜色的镀镍金属，搭配胡桃木和织物材料，配置成不同的收纳解决方案，适应不同生活空间的需求。模块化系统允许用户将其设置成侧板、架子、屏风、桌子、咖啡桌、电视柜和复杂的存储系统。由于这些配置不需要固定在墙壁上，用户可以在任何他们认为合适的地方自由使用和移动它们。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072201248ChoOE2zewPtlBYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.602344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072201254tMA92cpVhEfjv68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220124ieATYSnrhtqpvLJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220124o0XScj3rnA4qQbHR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220126ZMizFa8CRKb3PqLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.306250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220126eYPDBF04oancdV73.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.757031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.momocca.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Momocca</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>A Set of Cast Bronze Bookends by Josh Owen &amp; Wendell Castle</h3><p>罗切斯特理工学院工业设计系的教授、设计师 Josh Owen 和雕塑艺术家 Wendell Castle 合作，推出了一系列限量版铸铜书挡。</p><p>虽然两位设计师风格不一，各有独特的设计语言，但二者的创作融合在一起杂糅出一种表现力更多元的美感，两个产品能够组合使用，可以对话，添入了更多拓展想象力的空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220259VI93T6rjGzCdLWoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220259kFYW1h43ieaxInbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220259IVwqEAf5RcDZpCbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072202597APapkYw6WeirTB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220259VTUkG8je4mExwfcD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://shoponecollection.com/#bookends\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shoponecollection</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ideebebe by Sangwook Lee</h3><p>最近，众筹网站 Kickstarter 上线了一款一次性围兜 Ideebebe，出自设计师 Sangwook Lee 之手。有经验的母亲也许都遇到过类似的情况，婴幼儿容易流口水，吃饭容易洒出来弄脏衣物，围兜几乎是必需品，但也需要频繁清洗，但科学表明，经常重复使用的围兜容易成为细菌的滋生地，引起皮疹和刺激。</p><p>而 Ideebebe 具有高吸水性，并通过两个胶带粘在幼儿的衣服上。围兜是环保的，使用天然木丝和竹布制成，吸水性好，抗菌和低过敏性。产品可自然降解，一次性围兜对于婴幼儿来说也更健康，保持干爽洁净。组合装早鸟价 40 美元，点击这里尝试购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220352N8hGTpeIAMKxVZJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220352Oi9G725n14e3jl0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220352QwG5pvRnqoEPzBXc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220352Sdy6CiErlk2GWKej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072203520gdusftZTWb6QIRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/640759636/ideebebe-super-absorbent-l-convenient-l-soft-l-bib?ref=6ftq0p\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kickstarter</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Solair by Pushkin Sonkusare</h3><p>在室外晾衣绳上晾晒衣物，是一种有效且环保的方式。但碰上长期多云、多雨的天气就比较倒霉，不能保持清爽干燥，还有可能会遇到发霉的情况。</p><p>Solair 是一个不错的解决方案，这是设计师 Pushkin Sonkusare 推出的一款折叠式烘干机，看上去就像是为衣服专门搭建了一个小屋子，里面有循环的暖风和紫外线，确保衣物干燥干净。如果你住在常年晒不到太阳的屋子，Solair 说不定会帮上大忙。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220452hebdmf9qktapSnu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220451DmS365guNGUjsdpX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811072204518OZyt1xJMposCmAc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107220454XMLwolFzbvVgAekB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/11/06/the-next-best-thing-to-the-clothes-line/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}